  <main class="main">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section id="home" class="hero section">
      <!--<img src="/images/memary/cover3.jpg" srcset="/images/memary/cover2.jpg 1000w">-->
      <img src="/images/refragment01/key1_logo.png" alt="coverimage">
    </section><!-- /Hero Section -->

    <!-- Story Section -->
    <section id="story" class="services section">
      <!-- Story Title -->
      <div class="container section-title" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2>Story</h2>
      </div><!-- End Story Title -->
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row gy-4">
          <div class="col-10 col-xl-8 mx-auto text-left mainstory" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <p>Silverseal Private Academy is a pioneering model school where students have the unique opportunity 
              to shape their school environment through a democratic process. Decisions are made collectively 
              by voting, and those that secure a majority are enacted as policies.</p><br />
            <p><b>Kusaka Yuuma</b>, the main protagonist, is the treasurer of the student council. He works alongside 
              his childhood friend <b>Kuromiya Reika</b>, the popular and respected student council president who is 
              a ray of sunshine that attracts people wherever she goes.</p><br />
            <p>He lives a tranquil student life, blissfully unaware of the storm brewing on the horizon. 
              That is, until Reika unveils a new controversial policy that sparks widespread debate. 
              Disrupting their lives and turning their world upside down, changing everything they 
              once knew forever.</p><br />
            <p>
              This is the story of ambitious teenagers confronted with a reality far removed from 
              their expectations. Will they be able to navigate a life that sabotages them at every turn? 
              It all depends on “you”.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section><!-- /Story Section -->

    <!-- Concept Section -->
    <section id="concept" class="services section">
      <!-- Concept Title -->
      <div class="container section-title" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2>Concept</h2>
      </div><!-- End Concept Title -->
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row gy-4">
          <div class="col-10 col-xl-8 mx-auto text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <p><b>
              To you, who is drowning in despair.
            </b></p><br />
            <p>We all dream of a bright future ahead.<br />
              But life doesn't always turn out how you expected.<br />
              Harsh realities crush our spirits completely,<br />
              Leaving only disappointment and hopelessness.</p><br />
            <p>Re:Fragment is a story of young people full of dreams.<br />
              Our characters strive with all their might,<br />
              But things don't go as planned.<br />
              Their inexperience and naivety lead to mistakes.</p><br />
            <p>These young people have to live through painful days,<br />
              embracing their suffering, soothing their wounded hearts,<br />
              learning to live with loss, transforming it into a powerful drive,<br />
              preparing themselves for the journey of growing into adults.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section><!-- /Story Section -->

